							</p>
						</div>
				</div>
            </div>

			<div class="row">
                <div class="col-title col">
				<input type="checkbox" id="agreebox2" name="agreebox"><label for="agreebox2" class="text-default"><label class="col-agreetext">(필수)</label> 개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
				<div class="col-text col">
						<div class="form-text form-control overflow-auto">
